+# Word Garden
+
+Word Garden is a friendly terminal word-guessing game. Guess the hidden word before the garden runs out of water. It is like Hangman, but with plants instead of gallows.
+
+This is a small TUI game designed as a more cheerful alternative to Hangman. It is intended as a slightly more adventurous "Hello World" project for testing AI-assisted software development. The game includes input validation, state management, a simple loop, win/loss conditions, and a friendly terminal interface.
+
+## How to Play
+
+Start a new game:
+
+```bash
+python3 -m word_garden
+```
+
+You will see a hidden word represented as blanks. Guess letters one at a time. Correct guesses reveal the letter and help your garden grow. Incorrect guesses consume water and cause weeds to appear.
+
+Win by revealing the entire word before the garden runs out of water!
+
+## Options
+
+**Difficulty levels:**
+
+Choose how challenging the game should be:
+
+```bash
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty easy    # 8 water, 4–6 letter words
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty normal  # 6 water, 5–8 letter words (default)
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty hard    # 4 water, 7+ letter words
+```
+
+**ASCII mode:**
+
+If your terminal doesn't render emoji well, use ASCII-only output:
+
+```bash
+python3 -m word_garden --ascii
+```
+
+## Example Game
+
+```text
+🌱 Word Garden
+
+Word:      _ _ _ _ _ _
+Guessed:
+Water:     6/6 💧💧💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:     0
+
+Guess a letter: a
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+Word:      _ A _ _ _ _
+Guessed:   A
+Water:     6/6 💧💧💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:     0
+
+Guess a letter: z
+
+No match. A weed appears.
+
+Word:      _ A _ _ _ _
+Guessed:   A Z
+Water:     5/6 💧💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:     1 🌿
+
+Guess a letter: r
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+Word:      _ A R _ _ _
+Guessed:   A R Z
+Water:     5/6 💧💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:     1 🌿
+
+Guess a letter: g
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+Word:      G A R _ _ _
+Guessed:   A G R Z
+Water:     5/6 💧💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:     1 🌿
+
+Guess a letter: d
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+Word:      G A R D _ _
+Guessed:   A D G R Z
+Water:     5/6 💧💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:     1 🌿
+
+Guess a letter: e
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+Word:      G A R D E _
+Guessed:   A D E G R Z
+Water:     5/6 💧💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:     1 🌿
+
+Guess a letter: n
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+🌻 Bloom!
+
+You guessed the word: GARDEN
+The garden is thriving.
+```
+
+## Rules
+
+- **Valid input:** One letter at a time (a–z or A–Z). Input is converted to uppercase.
+- **Correct guess:** Reveals all matching positions. Doesn't cost water.
+- **Incorrect guess:** Costs 1 water and causes 1 weed to appear.
+- **Repeated guess:** Doesn't cost water or add weeds; shows a friendly reminder.
+- **Invalid input:** Doesn't consume a turn. You'll be re-prompted.
+- **Win:** Reveal the entire word before water reaches zero.
+- **Loss:** Water reaches zero before you guess the word.
+
+## Project Structure
+
+```
+word_garden/
+  __init__.py        – Package initialization
+  __main__.py        – Entry point for python3 -m word_garden
+  main.py            – Game loop and argument parsing
+  ui.py              – Terminal rendering (no I/O)
+  game.py            – Core game logic (no I/O)
+  words.py           – Word list and difficulty selection
+
+tests/
+  test_ui.py         – Tests for rendering
+  test_game.py       – Tests for game logic
+  test_words.py      – Tests for word selection
+```
+
+## Accessibility
+
+Word Garden is designed to be friendly and accessible:
+
+- Both emoji and ASCII-only modes are supported.
+- All numeric displays include text labels (e.g., "Water: 4/6").
+- Error messages are clear and specific.
+- Input is validated with helpful feedback.
+
+## Requirements
+
+- Python 3.11 or later
+- No external dependencies (stdlib only)
+
+## License
+
+Word Garden is released under the MIT License.
